Silas Gnaka (amụrụ na 18 Disemba 1998) bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ nke Ivorian nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-azụ azụ n'aka ekpe maka Belgian First Division A club K.A.S

Ngwaahịa Aspire Academy na Senegal, Gnaka bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta bọọlụ ọkachamara na klọb Belgian Eupen na Jenụwarị 2017. Ọ ghọrọ onye na-agbachitere aka ekpe maka klọb ahụ n'okpuru onye njikwa Claude Makélélé.
FC Magdeburg, nke e buliri n'ọkwa ọhụrụ na 2
Bundesliga, mara ọkwa na Gnaka ga-esonyere klọb ahụ maka oge 2022 na 23.
Gnaka malitere maka Ivory Coast U23s na egwuregwu abụọ nke 2019 Africa U-23 Cup of Nations na Machị 2019.
